<h2 class="heading mdl-typography--font-light">
Build your business for the future and partner with Google for Work
</h2>
<p>
We’ve designed the Google for Work Partner Program to enable you to sell,
service, and innovate by leveraging our products and platforms across the Google
for Work suite. Partners are a fundamental part of the Google for Work mission,
to empower billions of people to work the way they choose and build what’s next.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<figure class="image"></figure>
</div><a class="button-down gweb-smoothscroll-control" href=
"#program-tracks"><button class=
"mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--fab m-icon">keyboard_arrow_down</button></a>
</div>
<div class="maia-aux">
<div class="program-tracks section" id="program-tracks">
<h2 class="mdl-typography--font-light heading">
Program tracks
</h2>
<p class="subhead mdl-color-text--grey-500">
These are the available tracks for partners to choose from.
</p>
<div class="maia-cols cards-container">
<div class="maia-col-4 card services-track mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title"></div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
The Services Track
</h3>
<p>
The Services Track is for partners who provide services to customers, such as
selling, consulting, training, implementing and providing technical support for
Google for Work products.
</p>
</div>
<div class="mdl-card__actions">
<a class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect" href=
"services-track/benefits.html">Learn more</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="maia-col-4 card technology-track mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title"></div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
The Technology Track
</h3>
<p>
The Technology Track is for partners who create products that complement,
enhance or extend the reach or functionality of Google for Work products.
</p>
</div>
<div class="mdl-card__actions">
<a class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect" href=
"tech-track/benefits.html">Learn more</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="maia-col-4 card sales-track mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title"></div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
The Sales Track
</h3>
<p>
The Sales Track is for partners whose core competency is marketing and selling
Google for Work products at high volume.
</p>
<p class="mdl-color-text--grey-500">
This program is reserved for distributors and invited partners.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<aside class="maia-col-12 card referral-program side-media mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title"></div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
We also offer a Google Apps Referral Program.
</h3>
<p>
Recommend Apps to people you know and receive a reward for everyone who signs
up. <a data-g-action="Find out more" data-g-event="Work: Partners"
data-g-label="Home" href=
"../../work/apps/business/landing/partners/referral/">Find out more</a>.
</p>
</div>
</aside>

<div class="partner-programs section" id="partner-program">
<div class="maia-aux">
<h2 class="mdl-typography--font-light heading">
Program tracks
</h2>
<div class="card-container maia-cols">
<div class="maia-col-12 card partner side-media mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title">
<img alt="Google for Work Partner Badge" src=
"../../work/images/logo/googlework-partner.jpg">
</div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
The Partner Tier
</h3>
<p class="description">
The Google for Work Partner Program gives Partners access to a robust set of
resources to help them with their customers — everything from technical
resources to marketing and support.
</p>
<ul class="feature-list">
<li>Access to Google for Work Connect (Our one-stop community for partners to
access marketing campaigns, sales content, support resources and training)
</li>
<li>Console to manage customer accounts
</li>
<li>Use of the designated Google for Work Partner badge
</li>
<li>Discount on the list price of our suite of products
</li>
<li>Ongoing program communications
</li>
<li>Listing in our partner directory
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="maia-col-12 card partner-premier side-media mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
<div class="image mdl-card__title">
<img alt="Google for Work Partner Premier Badge" src=
"../../work/images/logo/googlework-partner-premier.jpg">
</div>
<div class="content mdl-card__supporting-text mdl-color-text--grey-800">
<h3 class="mdl-card__title-text subhead mdl-typography--font-regular">
The Premier Tier
</h3>
<p class="description">
The Premier Tier is reserved for Partners that have demonstrated higher levels
of competency and performance. Premier Partners receive <strong>further
exclusive opportunities and support</strong>, including:
</p>
<ul class="feature-list">
<li>All of the benefits available to partners
</li>
<li>Access to marketing funding
</li>
<li>Designated partner manager support
</li>
<li>Exclusive training and events
</li>
<li>Co-marketing opportunities with Google
</li>
<li>Use of the exclusive Premier Partner badge
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
